<TEXTAREA wrap=hard NAME="comment" ROWS="30" COLS="72" >Ataru@E'ciさんは No.6601「AnUndeadBardのlog（Patch後BardEpic）」で書きました。
>OldSebilisのTrakanon's Lairの中央にAnUndeadBardというMobがいます。
>WoodElfBRDからIndiff、一部PCからAppreらしかったです。
>ConcertHallのBBSの情報によればTrakanonKillから18-24hourでPopする模様。
>話してみます。
>
>You say, 'Hail An Undead Bard'
>An Undead Bard says 'Hail Ataru . Are you perchance a minstrel?' 
>
>You say, 'yes i am perchance a minstrel'
>An Undead Bard says 'I, too, am a bard, or was rather.  I have been 
>cursed by that blasted pile of bones who calls itself, Trakanon' 
>
>You say, 'what is Trakanon ?'
>An Undead Bard says 'He is the undead dragon who rules this realm.  I 
>came on a quest seeking strings for my new instrument.' 
>
>You say, 'what is your new instrument ?'
>An Undead Bard says 'I sought to create a Magical Lute.' 
>
>You say, 'what is a magical lute ?'
>An Undead Bard says 'One that would make me the greatest bard in all 
>the lands!  Are you on a similar quest?' 
>
>You say, 'yes i am on a similar quest'
>An Undead Bard says 'Well then, I would ask you a favor for one in 
>return.  If I bring that cursed dragon here, will you kill it for 
>me?' 
>
>You say, 'yes i will kill it for you'
>An Undead Bard says 'Excellent. I have stayed here far too long and I 
>wish to go to my eternal slumber. But before I do so, I ask for one 
>last request' 
>
>You say, 'what is last request ?'
>An Undead Bard says 'Give me the Mystical Lute Body you have.  I will 
>return it, don't worry. I only wish to hold an instrument one last 
>time before I leave.' 
</TEXTAREA><br>
</td></tr>
